node.text:
Dedicating my FIRST EVER IGTV to my 3 year old daughter, all in the name of #toddlertemptationchallenge 😂 It is rare that I share my children on this page, so enjoy this cutie pie & her 2 minute journey to resist sprinkle temptation. 😂😍 Also, baby girl, you’re not alone, mommy talks to her sprinkles too. 😉😍
.
.
.
.

node.text: Another all time favorite from Christmas past! 🥰 Also wanted to thank you guys for all the love on my last post! We are over the moon over here & it’s so fun to be able to share that with you all! 🤗🤗

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Rachel Fujihara on December 10, 2020 tagging @stephryanphoto. May be an image of 1 person, baby, standing and outerwear.

node.text: A lot of you have noticed things have been  pretty quiet around here lately, and I SO appreciate all the messages and sentiments so many of you have sent. 😌🥰 All is well...we are praising the Lord as we are pregnant with our third baby girl!! We have been trying for this baby for over 3 and a half years, so to say we are overjoyed would be an understatement! 😄 Since caking has always been a distraction/place holder, if you will from not getting pregnant, now that we finally are, I just have very little cake motivation. 😅 I’m not gone forever, but I don’t think I’ll be “back” quite how I was for a long time. I plan to enjoy every aspect of this pregnancy/baby as much as I can as it’s been very long awaited. 🥰🥰🥰 Thanks for being here with us! 😃
